beer.beer_description: A take on a federation era recipe, Australian Malt, US Cluster Hops and English Yeast.
Remix of the Mr Albert Stout, aged in a rum oak barrel for 6 months. The rum leaches groom the wood and into the beer, adding flavour and ABV.
